\cf0 Architectural & Process Summary\
\pard\pardeftab720\ri0\sl300\slmult1\sa225\partightenfactor0

\f0\b0\fs22 \cf0 This document serves as the foundational source of truth for the software development lifecycle, process governance, and technical architecture of the Homeflow native iOS mobile application. It demonstrates how high\uc0\u8209 level business discovery is bridged into a disciplined, AI\u8209 assisted engineering pipeline with spec\u8209 driven controls, objective evidence, and production\u8209 ready operational practices.\
\pard\pardeftab720\ri0\sb400\sa240\partightenfactor0

\f1\b\fs36 \cf0 1. Process Governance & Specification Framework\
\pard\pardeftab720\ri0\sl300\slmult1\sa240\partightenfactor0

\f0\b0\fs22 \cf0 To ensure deterministic outputs from AI agents and maintain high-grade quality control, a strict Spec-Driven Development lifecycle has been adopted. This eliminates ad-hoc development or "vibe coding" by establishing formal contracts before any code generation occurs.\
\pard\pardeftab720\ri0\sb400\sa240\partightenfactor0

\f1\b\fs28 \cf0 1.1 Core Repository Artifacts\
\pard\pardeftab720\ri0\sl300\slmult1\partightenfactor0

\f0\b0\fs22 \cf0 Four primary documentation artifacts will reside directly in version control alongside the source code, serving as the immutable source of truth for both human operators and AI agents:\
\pard\tx240\tx960\pardeftab720\li960\fi-360\ri0\sl300\slmult1\partightenfactor0
\ls1\ilvl0\cf0 {\listtext	\'95	}\uc0\u9679 	
\f1\b Project Constitution (constitution.md):
\f0\b0  Establishes the non-negotiable architectural, security, accessibility, and operational laws governing the entire codebase.\
{\listtext	\'95	}\uc0\u9679 	
\f1\b Domain Glossary (glossary.md):
\f0\b0  Maps out domain-specific logic, constraints, and business language definitions (e.g., winterization checklist items, task delegations, accessibility guidelines) to eliminate LLM ambiguity.\
{\listtext	\'95	}\uc0\u9679 	
\f1\b Feature Specifications (spec.md):
\f0\b0  Focuses entirely on the "What" and "Why" from a Product Owner perspective, detailing user personas (such as aging parents), multi-generational workflows, and strict acceptance criteria.\
{\listtext	\'95	}\uc0\u9679 	
\f1\b Technical Plans (plan.md):
\f0\b0  Generated by the AI and approved by the Human-in-the-Loop, detailing database schema modifications, API payloads, and discrete task breakdowns.\
\pard\pardeftab720\ri0\sb320\sa200\partightenfactor0
\ls1\ilvl0
