\ls1\ilvl0
\fs20 \cf0 {\listtext	\'95	}In this framework, Verification focuses on whether the implementation faithfully matches the specified requirements, and Validation confirms that the Intended Use can be reliably achieved by the users. \
\pard\pardeftab720\ri0\sl300\slmult1\sb120\sa240\partightenfactor0
\ls1\ilvl0\cf0 {\listtext	\'95	}Every feature specification requires an explicit section for Intended Use and a Risk/Hazard Classification detailing failure modes and software mitigations, which are then traced through the Technical Plan, source code, verification tests, and validation activities.\
\
\pard\pardeftab720\ri0\sl300\slmult1\sb320\sa200\partightenfactor0
\ls1\ilvl0
\f1\b\fs28 \cf0 {\listtext	\'95	}1.3 Example End\uc0\u8209 to\u8209 End Flow
\f0\b0\fs22 \
\pard\pardeftab720\ri0\sl300\slmult1\sb225\sa225\partightenfactor0
\ls1\ilvl0\cf0 {\listtext	\'95	}For example, consider the \'93
\f1\b Shared Winterization Task Checklist
\f0\b0 \'94 feature. \
\pard\tx360\tx1080\pardeftab720\li1080\fi-360\ri0\sl300\slmult1\partightenfactor0
\ls2\ilvl0\cf0 {\listtext	\'95	}\uc0\u9679 	A non\u8209 negotiable rule in the Project Constitution requires that any cross\u8209 user state changes are atomic and auditable. \
{\listtext	\'95	}\uc0\u9679 	The Feature Specification defines the Intended Use, multi\u8209 generational user personas, and acceptance criteria for shared task assignment, completion, and notification flows. \
{\listtext	\'95	}\uc0\u9679 	From that spec, the AI generates a Technical Plan that proposes specific Supabase tables, row\u8209 level security policies, and SwiftUI view models, which are reviewed and approved by a human operator. \
{\listtext	\'95	}\uc0\u9679 	The resulting implementation is verified by automated unit and integration tests (XCTest) along with device\u8209 level UI tests (XCUITest) running in CI, and validated via structured usability sessions to ensure that users can reliably complete critical winterization tasks.\
\pard\pardeftab720\ri0\sl300\slmult1\sb320\sa200\partightenfactor0
\ls2\ilvl0
\f1\b\fs28 \cf0 {\listtext	\'95	}1.4 Hierarchy of Truth
\f0\b0\fs22 \
\pard\pardeftab720\ri0\sl300\slmult1\sb225\sa225\partightenfactor0
\ls2\ilvl0\cf0 {\listtext	\'95	}To keep both human operators and AI agents aligned, the repository follows a strict Hierarchy of Truth. If conflicts arise, higher\uc0\u8209 order artifacts will take precedence over lower\u8209 order ones.\
\pard\tx360\tx1080\pardeftab720\li1080\fi-360\ri0\sl300\slmult1\partightenfactor0
\ls3\ilvl0\cf0 {\listtext	1.	}1.	
\f1\b Project Constitution 
\f0\b0 (constitution.md)\
\pard\tx1080\tx1800\pardeftab720\li1800\fi-360\ri0\sl300\slmult1\partightenfactor0
\ls4\ilvl0\cf0 {\listtext	\'95	}\uc0\u9679 	Defines non-negotiable architectural, security, accessibility, and operational laws.\
{\listtext	\'95	}\uc0\u9679 	No specification, plan, or implementation may contradict the Constitution.\
\pard\tx360\tx1080\pardeftab720\li1080\fi-360\ri0\sl300\slmult1\partightenfactor0
\ls5\ilvl0\cf0 {\listtext	1.	}2.	
\f1\b Domain Glossary
\f0\b0  (\cf3 glossary.md\cf0 )\
\pard\tx1080\tx1800\pardeftab720\li1800\fi-360\ri0\sl300\slmult1\partightenfactor0
\ls6\ilvl0\cf0 {\listtext	\'95	}\uc0\u9679 	Standardizes domain terminology, constraints, and business language.\
{\listtext	\'95	}\uc0\u9679 	If wording in specs or plans is ambiguous, the Glossary definition is authoritative.\
\pard\tx360\tx1080\pardeftab720\li1080\fi-360\ri0\sl300\slmult1\partightenfactor0
\ls7\ilvl0\cf0 {\listtext	1.	}3.	
\f1\b Feature Specifications
\f0\b0  (\cf3 spec.md\cf0 )\
\pard\tx1080\tx1800\pardeftab720\li1800\fi-360\ri0\sl300\slmult1\partightenfactor0
\ls8\ilvl0\cf0 {\listtext	\'95	}\uc0\u9679 	Describe the "What" and "Why" from a Product Owner perspective, including Intended Use,personas, acceptance criteria, and risk classifications.\
{\listtext	\'95	}\uc0\u9679 	Technical Plans and implementations must satisfy constraints defined here.\
\pard\tx360\tx1080\pardeftab720\li1080\fi-360\ri0\sl300\slmult1\partightenfactor0
\ls9\ilvl0\cf0 {\listtext	1.	}4.	
\f1\b Technical Plans
\f0\b0  (plan.md)\
\pard\tx1080\tx1800\pardeftab720\li1800\fi-360\ri0\sl300\slmult1\partightenfactor0
\ls10\ilvl0\cf0 {\listtext	\'95	}\uc0\u9679 	Translate Feature Specifications into concrete data models, API contracts, and task breakdowns under the constraints of the Constitution and Glossary.\
{\listtext	\'95	}\uc0\u9679 	Source code conforms to the plan or the plan must be updated & re-approved.\
\pard\tx360\tx1080\pardeftab720\li1080\fi-360\ri0\sl300\slmult1\partightenfactor0
